{"tid":1687664,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：我叫習近平煤山吊頸，有目標有遠景；泛民連登就叫曱近平，純粹洩憤。","createTime":"2019-11-02T03:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T11:13:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":29,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7cffdc340a5a488cf428e18dab90b52505304a11","tid":1687664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我叫習近平煤山吊頸，有目標有遠景；泛民連登就叫曱近平，純粹洩憤。這叫話語圈之完成啊。衙差叫市民做蟑螂曱甴，現在市民叫習近平做蟑螂曱甴，就完成了衙差對市民詛咒的合理性。連香港人都用蟑螂來罵中共領導人，證明蟑螂是普遍的咒罵詞，差人沒有歧視香港人了。這叫rounding up the discourse loop，話語圈之完成。你死撚咗都唔知mer事。<br />\n泛民連登是這樣操作心理技術及完成民俗詛咒的。惡毒到不得了。香港人，睇少一陣陳雲，都會被泛民暗共謀害，死了也不知道是什麼原因。好似泛民的民主中國論，就害死兩代香港人。泛民是共產黨的暗底，大家知道的吧？<br />\n（圖片來源：網絡）"},{"pid":"e6cc73e42755e8b6a997736e57a2360896645b0e","tid":1687664,"uid":15605,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"憨撚鳩"},{"pid":"a4be1eb283df7ef69a99702b75a1c38697331fa2","tid":1687664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dcc725e080279c245a02797aa980b658eb2c93","tid":1687664,"uid":153811,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"你寫左封信寄去香港同大陸政府機構先啦，臭閪。"},{"pid":"464bc9f6fb37bf6fc66b3671e0da2af85f6afbb8","tid":1687664,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n甴種平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9269007fc6372529ead13e3ea6709df12f5d2c5a","tid":1687664,"uid":58971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"食藥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af4308c510182166b562fe32f95ae9ac2a4fd9d","tid":1687664,"uid":156511,"like":3,"dislik